# Page Review Protocol

When the user asks to review or rate a page (1-10 or otherwise):

1. **Read the entire page first.** Have the full content in context before forming any opinion.
2. Never rate based on partial reads, summaries, or memory from earlier in the conversation.
3. If the page is too long for a single read, use multiple reads or a subagent to ensure full coverage.
